  "transparency": {
    "explainability": "high",
    "explanation": "This signal identifies cohorts (minimum 1,000 individuals) who have engaged with health content related to specific chronic conditions. Data is collected from opt-in health apps, pharmacy loyalty programs, and patient education platforms. All data is de-identified using HIPAA Safe Harbor method before aggregation. No individual health information (PHI) is ever available. Cohorts are built based on aggregated engagement patterns with health content, not individual diagnoses. Designed exclusively for disease awareness and patient education, not direct product promotion. Approved only for FDA/EMA-compliant educational campaigns.",
